'''Acceleration Team France''' is the [[France|French]] team of [[Formula Acceleration 1]], an international racing series. They are run by the Belgian [[Azerti Motorsport]] team,<ref name="POR">{{cite web|url=http://acceleration14.com/entry-list-portugal |title=ENTRY LIST &#124; Acceleration |publisher=Acceleration14.com |date= |accessdate=2014-04-28}}</ref> owned by [[Wim Coekelbergs]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://acceleration14.com/fa1-line-0 |title=FA1 LINE-UP &#124; Acceleration |publisher=Acceleration14.com |date=2014-03-03 |accessdate=2014-04-28}}</ref>

== History ==

=== 2014 season ===
'''''Drivers:''' [[Sergio Campana (racing driver)|Sergio Campana]], [[Nathanaël Berthon]]''

The team announced Italian driver Sergio Campana as their driver for the inaugural Formula Acceleration 1 round in Portimao.<ref name=POR /> He moved to the [[Acceleration Team Portugal|Portuguese team]] for round 2 in Navarra and was replaced by [[Nathanaël Berthon]].

